bf80c982-4f84-4594-8509-16f4ae93145d	Blueberry Shake	blueberry-shake	Real food, the way Earth made it, has always been enough. Our Blueberry Shake brings that truth to your day, crafted with the simple goodness of whole blueberries. We don't strip food down to numbers or add in anything synthetic; instead, we take real, honest berries and slow-crush them, keeping all the good fats, fibre, and natural micronutrients intact. It's the nourishment your body remembers, designed to fit into a modern, full life without compromise.\n\nThis isn't a quick fix or a processed drink playing a numbers game. It's steady, real energy and honest goodness, perfect for an everyday ritual. Each bottle is a quiet contrast to a world obsessed with taking things out of food, only to sell them back as separate supplements. With SOAKD, you get blueberries as they were meant to be — whole, rich in natural antioxidants, and simply delicious.\n\nTaste the difference that comes from patience and respect for ingredients. We invite you to make this honest shake a part of your day, and feel the gentle strength that comes from truly whole food.	19b4e330-d4a1-4a34-a6bd-64808c5fb275	https://oiblxqrvyekxdbimvhod.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/product-images/4swma3vcho_1781436961650.png	{}	published	t	0	Blueberry Shake — Whole-Food, Slow-Crushed | SOAKD	Our Blueberry Shake brings whole, slow-crushed blueberries to your day. Real food, with natural antioxidants and fibre, just as Earth made it.	2026-06-14 11:36:12.442+00	bab29fff-0265-477a-9a7b-16f1af9007a6	bab29fff-0265-477a-9a7b-16f1af9007a6	2026-06-14 11:36:12.581995+00	2026-07-09 10:11:44.523223+00	150.00	120.00	#9575ab	a0000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001	f	0	\N	f	SKU100000025	2	0	\N
1648a152-7536-4564-86c6-c611745b712a	The Original Ragda	almond-milk	Long before protein came in a tub, strength was built on real, whole food. Our Almond Milk, "The Original Ragda," brings that nourishment back, inspired by ancient wrestling diets where every ingredient served a purpose. Inside each bottle, you'll find a precise blend of 12 almonds, 8g hemp hearts, 10g melon seeds, 4g poppy seeds, and 5g pumpkin seeds – whole ingredients crushed slowly, the way Earth made it.\n\nWe don't strip food down to numbers or rely on isolates. Instead, we keep the good fats, fibre, and micronutrients intact, gently infusing fennel, black pepper, elaichi, and rose petals to make it easy on your gut. Our ingredients are crushed using a stone mortar and neem wood pestle, an ancient method that protects the delicate oils and enzymes, ensuring you get real recovery that's rich in protein, fibre, magnesium, calcium, iron, and zinc.\n\nThis isn't a quick fix; it's steady, honest nourishment designed for your everyday ritual. It’s what happens when patience meets purpose, creating a drink that’s as cooling and hydrating as it is nutrient-dense. Taste it, and tell us how it sits with you – we'd genuinely love to hear.	f772fe5d-fd9f-4868-bebc-5faba5a668fa	https://oiblxqrvyekxdbimvhod.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/product-images/eseglz1avd_1781206316681.png	{}	published	t	0	The Original Ragda Almond Milk — Whole Food Nourishment | SOAKD	Experience The Original Ragda, a stone-crushed almond milk with whole hemp, melon, poppy, and pumpkin seeds. Real, slow nourishment, the way Earth made it.	2026-06-06 10:38:27.688+00	bab29fff-0265-477a-9a7b-16f1af9007a6	bab29fff-0265-477a-9a7b-16f1af9007a6	2026-06-06 10:38:27.839498+00	2026-07-09 10:11:44.523223+00	150.00	130.00	#e09771	a0000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001	f	0	\N	f	SKU100000017	1	2	\N
