2e8c6701-00b4-43cf-95bf-52eece23659c	almond shake	almond-shake	Sometimes, the simplest things are the ones we miss most. Our almond shake brings back that feeling of real nourishment, the way Earth made it. We start with whole, sun-ripened almonds, slowly stone-crushed to release all their goodness – the natural fats, the subtle sweetness, the gentle protein. It’s a quiet contrast to drinks that strip food down to numbers, leaving nothing real behind. Here, everything stays whole.\n\nThis isn't about chasing fleeting trends; it's about steady, honest fuel for your day. Drink it in the morning for a calm start, or as a gentle pick-me-up when you need something real. It’s just whole food, treated with patience, made to fit into a life that moves fast but still craves something true.\n\nWe believe that healthy means whole, familiar, and kind to your body, not complex or clinical. Taste the difference that comes from keeping things as they should be, and let this almond shake be a simple, grounding part of your everyday ritual. We'd love to hear how it sits with you.	2ca5e437-fc39-43e6-9ae5-9b0896cc8b7b	https://oiblxqrvyekxdbimvhod.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/product-images/ul3ekdluii_1783445109445.webp	{}	published	f	0	Almond Shake — Whole, Stone-Crushed Nourishment | WHOLESIP	Experience real nourishment with our whole almond shake, slowly stone-crushed. Honest, steady fuel for your day, the way Earth made it.	2026-07-07 17:25:55.409+00	ba7b59a1-d51a-49ed-9ae3-cf0737cc0c83	ba7b59a1-d51a-49ed-9ae3-cf0737cc0c83	2026-07-07 17:25:55.549778+00	2026-07-11 13:19:45.65662+00	80.00	70.00	\N	156c8c4f-4aae-4bff-8f29-4ac24d4805f5	t	28	5	f	SKU100100148	14	0	20ebadab-e4f4-4e8a-b728-d1f82f07ea05
